The W space SOCWR formulation follows the Jabr second-order cone relaxation
(R. A. Jabr, 2006) as implemented in PowerModels.jl
(https://github.com/lanl-ansi/PowerModels.jl, BSD 3-Clause). PowerModels.jl was
used as a formulation reference; the tellegen implementation is independent.

